summary: As much as I would love for Pikachu to say ‘fuck’ I am hoping Detective Pikachu is the softest PG-13 movie we’ve seen in...
body:
As much as I would love for Pikachu to say ‘fuck’ I am hoping Detective Pikachu is the softest PG-13 movie we’ve seen in decades. I hope it’s the 90s equivalent of PG because the kidlets deserve this one too. Millennial parents deserve to see their young kids’ joy without getting any side eye.

Pokémon the Movie 2000 snuck in a joke about STDs I’m sure there’ll be fun stuff for the adults without Pikachu telling someone to fuck off.

summary: I’m definitely skipping Let’s Go Eevee. After the hype of Pokémon Go, I didn’t really like the mechanics. I’m just gonna wait...
body:
I’m definitely skipping Let’s Go Eevee. After the hype of Pokémon Go, I didn’t really like the mechanics. I’m just gonna wait for Gen 8 next year.

On a side thing tho, even though I don’t want to, I’m heavily tempted to watch Detective Pikachu. It reminds me of that Sonic fan trailer years ago but more polished.
